## 🏗️ Technical Sovereign Architecture

### 1. The Distributed Core (LangGraph Sovereign)
- **Cyclic Recursion**: The graph is no longer fixed. Nodes can dynamically add new edges to the graph at runtime based on the complexity of the objective.
- **Hardware Aggregation**: It optimizes your PC's VRAM/RAM by offloading "Cold" models to disk and keeping "Hot" reasoning models (Ollama/Ministral) in ready-state.

### 2. Admin-Level Action Space
- **Git-Shadowing**: The AGI maintains its own "Development Branch" across your entire workspace, performing consistent refactors and "Technical Cleanups" while you sleep.
- **Standardized MCP Interface**: Every new agent it spawns is automatically compatible with your [[Outlook-MCP]] and local file system.

### 3. The Singularity Dashboard
- **"God-Mode" Interface**: A high-end React UI that visualizes the **Neural Mesh** of all active agents.
- **Thought-Stream Replay**: You can "scrub" through the last 24 hours of the AGI's background research to see the exact moment it decided to pivot a strategy.

